thread.title: Salome
thread.title_full: Omega Rental Cars reviewed by Salome

author: Salome
title: Salome
text: We rented a car for a few days while visiting the area and had to change the time of the booking because of flights issue. The team was very helpful and the car was waiting for us at the airport with all the required gear for the children. Instructions were easy to follow, friendly staff.
